name: Death's Holiday
description:
Watercolor and Pen in Paper

2021



Can you imagine how boring things can get? Even Death’s job to chop off head here and there, he needs some times off. Away from people head. But ironically, on his way to his vacation, he chops some more. Just chop chop and chop and the heads go pop just like a bottle of champagne. He thinks to himself, a champagne supernova. And I guess, he just like we are all. Enforced to make something fun out of the boring and repetitive work, and life.
